'''夏利里拉家族'''是一個源自[[英屬印度|英屬印度]][[信德族|信德族]]的[[香港|香港]]富豪[[家族|家族]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cityu.edu.hk/sites/g/files/asqsls3821/files/2019-06/e_Harilela.pdf|title=Mr David HARILELA|publisher=City University of Hong Kong|access-date=2020-04-10|archive-date=2022-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220307193553/https://www.cityu.edu.hk/sites/g/files/asqsls3821/files/2019-06/e_Harilela.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cityu.edu.hk/sites/g/files/asqsls3821/files/2019-06/c_Harilela.pdf|title=Mr David HARILELA|publisher=City University of Hong Kong|access-date=2020-04-10|archive-date=2022-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220302030721/https://www.cityu.edu.hk/sites/g/files/asqsls3821/files/2019-06/c_Harilela.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_557798_0|title=曾蔭權暫時甩難 裁決前「最後晚餐」|publisher=壹週刊|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410232126/https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_557798_0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2004/10/21/HK0410210078.htm|title=印裔首富夏利里拉豪門爭產|publisher=文匯報|date=2004-10-21|accessdate=2009-07-03|archive-date=2008-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527055016/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2004/10/21/HK0410210078.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

「夏利里拉」這個姓氏只在香港出現，起源於尼雲斯的父母名字。根據週刊的訪問，當年尼雲斯從[[英屬印度|英屬印度]]來香港打工，母親不幸在家鄉病逝，而當地的家人在未等及尼雲斯回鄉就急忙把她火化，使尼雲斯非常不滿。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hk.nextmgz.com/nextbook/ebook/0q1RMUse|title=夏利里拉家族|publisher=壹週刊|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2020-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200410232127/https://hk.nextmgz.com/nextbook/ebook/0q1RMUse|dead-url=no}}</ref>  因此，尼雲斯決定把父、母親的名字（Haribai 和 Lilaram）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://webb-site.com/dbpub/natperson.asp?p=26807|title=Harilela, Naroomal Lilaram|publisher=Webb-site Who's Who|accessdate=2020-04-10|archive-date=2016-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603140706/https://webb-site.com/dbpub/natperson.asp?p=26807|dead-url=no}}</ref> 合成一個新的姓氏，並從此成為其家族的姓氏。其[[夏利萊大宅|家族大宅]]內設有傳統宗教廟堂，信奉印度教及基督教等各宗教的家族人士均可入內。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://s3.us-west-1.wasabisys.com/pl-library/books/ac0612f5b7a46bef35d035b7bb1f3d0b.pdf|title=香港百人∙下冊 (頁320-325)|publisher=亞洲電視|access-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423195339/https://s3.us-west-1.wasabisys.com/pl-library/books/ac0612f5b7a46bef35d035b7bb1f3d0b.pdf|archive-date=2020-04-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

1996年，[[夏利萊|夏利萊]]及[[夏加利|夏加利]]兄弟二人成為[[香港特別行政區第一屆政府推選委員會|香港特別行政區第一屆政府推選委員會]]成員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rediff.com/news/jan/03hong.htm|title=Indians anxious about Chinese takeover of Hong Kong|publisher=The Rediff Special|accessdate=2020-04-23|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091711/http://www.rediff.com/news/jan/03hong.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[夏利萊|夏利萊]]及[[夏加利|夏加利]]兄弟二人先後擔任[[尼日尔|尼日尔]]駐香港名譽領事。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060718011850/https://www.protocol.gov.hk/chi/consular/africa/niger.htm|title=政府總部禮賓處 - 領館及官方認可機構 - 尼日爾|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2006-07-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423200442/https://www.protocol.gov.hk/chi/consular/africa/niger.htm|title=政府總部禮賓處 - 領館及官方認可機構 - 尼日爾|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2020-04-23}}</ref> 2006年11月，[[夏加利|夏加利]]成為[[香港旅遊發展局|香港旅遊發展局]]成員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200610/31/P200610310201.htm|title=委任香港旅遊發展局成員|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2006-10-31|accessdate=2020-04-23|archive-date=2019-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190902183857/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200610/31/P200610310201.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[夏利博|夏利博]]及[[夏偉基|夏偉基]]父子二人分別擔任[[马尔代夫|马尔代夫]]駐香港名譽領事及名譽副領事。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060617203950/https://www.protocol.gov.hk/chi/consular/asia/maldives.htm|title=政府總部禮賓處 - 領館及官方認可機構 - 馬爾代夫|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2006-06-17}}</ref> [[夏雅朗|夏雅朗]]先後出任[[方便營商諮詢委員會|方便營商諮詢委員會]]（方諮會）非官方委員、[[亞太經合組織|亞太經合組織]][[商貿諮詢理事會|商貿諮詢理事會]]中國香港替補代表、[[審查貪污舉報諮詢委員會|審查貪污舉報諮詢委員會]]非官方委員、[[團結香港基金|團結香港基金]]參事、以及[[香港總商會|香港總商會]]主席。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200801/10/P200801090184.htm|title=政府委任方便營商諮詢委員會成員|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2008-01-10|accessdate=2020-04-23|archive-date=2019-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007024459/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200801/10/P200801090184.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201812/19/P2018121900414.htm|title=政府委任亞太經合組織商貿諮詢理事會中國香港代表|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2018-12-19|accessdate=2020-04-23|archive-date=2019-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107095628/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201812/19/P2018121900414.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201912/27/P2019122700646.htm|title=政府委任廉政公署相關委員會非官方成員|publisher=香港特別行政區政府|date=2019-12-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516095839/https://www.chamber.org.hk/en/media/press-releases_detail.aspx?ID=3611|title=Aron Harilela Elected HKGCC Chairman|publisher=The Hong Kong General Chamber of Commerce}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200503100601/scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3082611/hong-kong-chamber-chief-aron-harilela-calls-early-dialogue|title=Hong Kong chamber chief Aron Harilela calls for early dialogue with Beijing to settle 'post-2047 uncertainty'|publisher=South China Morning Post}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619010643/scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/2151236/plan-bulldoze-and-develop-hong-kong-golf-club|title=Plan to bulldoze and develop Hong Kong Golf Club in Fanling 'a bit of a red herring', says leader of city's biggest business chamber|publisher=South China Morning Post}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.wenweipo.com/2019/11/29/IN1911290014.htm|title=港總商會主席：美涉港法案增香港營商環境不確定性|publisher=文匯報}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110014343/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2014/12/31/HK1412310029.htm|title=戰後軍營生意賺第一桶金　　身家百億|publisher=文匯報}}</ref>

